                  <h3>CAREER GUIDANCE WORKSHOP.</h3>
                   <p>Aakriti organised career guidance workshop for girls in January 2014. The students were given guidance and introductions to various competitive examinations for post graduation in India and abroad. Examinations including GRE, GMAT, TOEFL, CAT, GATE, IELTS and TANCET were covered. Guidance about civil services examinations was also given. The workshop was a good success as the girls of CEG showed active participation in the workshop.</p>
                </div>
